{"word":"G4938 - σύντριμμα - sýntrimma - soon-trim'-mah - Destruction","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύντριμμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sýntrimma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>soon-trim'-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Destruction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நாசம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. that which is broken or shattered, a fracture"},{"paragraph":"2. calamity, ruin, destruction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4937 - συντρίβω - syntríbō - soon-tree'-bo/4937\">G4937</a>; <i>concussion</i> or utter <i>fracture</i> (properly concretely), that is, complete <i>ruin:</i> - destruction."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4937 - συντρίβω - syntríbō - soon-tree'-bo/4937\">G4937</a>, <a href=\"#/G4938 - σύντριμμα - sýntrimma - soon-trim'-mah/4938\">G4938</a>"}]}